ay, Apayao (photos), Aurora (photos), Batangas, Cagayan, Camarines, Camarines Sur, Isabela, Laguna, Quezon, Rizal, Sorsogon, MARINDUQUE, MASBATE, MINDANAO: Agusan del Norte, Agusan del Sur, Bukidnon, Cotabato, Davao, Davao del Sur, Lanao del Sur, Misamis, Misamis Occidental, Zamboanga, Zamboanga del Sur, MINDORO, PALAWAN, PANAY, SAMAR, SIARGAO, SULU ARCHIPELAGO, TICAO.", "notes": "In Luzon from Cagayan to Sorsogon. Common in primary forests at low and medium elevation. 0m to 100m (photos).", "conservation_status": "Least Concern (IUCN 3.1).", "dao_category": "", "other_fields": {}, "gallery_url": "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/cgi-bin/bhbase/cubic_gallery_public.pl?start_at=0&taxon_name=Diplodiscus+paniculatus", "thumbs": ["http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/6_22_11/22jun11/Diplodiscuspaniculatus.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/6_22_11/22jun11/Diplodiscuspaniculatus1.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/6_22_11/22jun11/Diplodiscuspaniculatus2.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/6_22_11/22jun11/Diplodiscuspaniculatus3.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/8_28_11_1/25aug11a/Diplodiscuspaniculatus.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/8_28_11_1/25aug11a/Diplodiscuspaniculatus1.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/8_28_11_1/25aug11a/Diplodiscuspaniculatus2.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/8_14_14/14aug14/DSC_0669.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/8_14_14/14aug14/DSC_0665.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/8_14_14/14aug14/DSC_0667.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/8_14_14/14aug14/DSC_0659.j